<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungmuonna kim kipahna kim
 Hehpihna vak ka Lal melah
 Pulthuok a nem thuok laia nem
 Vakvaite din In nuom.

[V2]
 2. A umna mun cheng van ahi
 A keng bula um hi a nuom
 Lungkhamna leh thim nuoia chau
 Nuomin a chawlhsak sek.

[V3]
 3. Suihlung ahel ka sa lei ah,
 Mahleh hehpihna Lal vangin;
 Ka lautha lungdeihte haw tawh,
 Nunnuom in leng tan au.

[V4]
 4. Aw, I mi ngaihteu chieh ka mui,
 Hehpihna vakah a leng ui;
 A mau a mihiem hin beita,
 Angelte dungsun in,

[V5]
 5. Ka hun ngai Aw, kipahna pen,
 Na thawkna chun kah lai a nem;
 Ka lenna gamgaw gam ahi,
 Hun khen ding ka ngam puoi.</lyrics>
<title>Vakvaite In</title>
<hymn_number>294</hymn_number>
<author>Kamlala</author>
</song>